#

Greek Burger

25 min
$12.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A juicy burger infused with bold flavors from feta cheese and fresh herbs, served with a creamy tzatziki sauce.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/4 tsp
  • burger buns: 4
  • tzatziki sauce: 1/2 cup
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 1
